{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"selected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indeterminate"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Suggestions","anchor":"Suggestions","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox\/b\/6578e5\/t\/3dd013a529"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Business Tools","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeBusinessTools"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Version","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.3.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"type":"aside"},{"name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"